    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルーク</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Luke</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あー助かった！
ミラクルグミのおかげで全快だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ahhh, I'm saved!
I'm totally recovered thanks to that Miracle Gummi!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとうな、ルーク。
お前、案外いいとこあるんだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thanks a bunch, Luke. There're actually
some surprsingly nice things about you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだろう？
ルークは悪いとこばかりじゃないんだ。
わかってもらえて嬉しいよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right? Luke isn't just all bad. I'm glad you get it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>べつに。
うちの屋敷で大量に腐らせてるしな
ミラクルグミなんて</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It wasn't a big deal.
I've got loads of Miracle Gummis
just sitting around rotting in my mansion, anyway.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>つうかむしろ
俺にとってはアップルグミのが珍しいっつの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really, if anything, Apple Gummis
are more of a rarity to me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱり嫌な奴かも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Actually, he really might just
be an unlikeable guy...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……そうだな。　前言撤回だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Yeah. I take back what I said.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
